        public java.lang.Object newClassInstance(java.lang.Class className,

                                  throws java.lang.RuntimeException
        Create a proxy instance that implements the specified access interface and delegates incoming invocations to the specified dynamic implementation. The dynamic implementation may change at run-time, and the proxy will always delegates to the up-to-date implementation.
        Parameters:

        implClassName - the backend dynamic implementation
